@startuml
title CLI Interface — Class Diagram (issue #391)

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class Calculator {
  .. Binary Operations ..
  + add(a, b)
  + subtract(a, b)
  + multiply(a, b)
  + divide(a, b): float
  + power(base, exponent)
  .. Unary Operations ..
  + factorial(n: int): int
  + square(x): int|float
  + cube(x): int|float
  + sqrt(x): float
  + cbrt(x): float
  + log10(x): float
  + ln(x): float
}

class OperationRegistry {
  - _calculator: Calculator
  - _operations: dict[str, int]
  - _sorted_names: List[str]
  --
  + __init__(calculator: Calculator)
  + get_operations(): List[str]
  + get_arity(operation_name: str): int
  + call(operation_name: str, *args): Any
}

package "cli (module)" {
  class parse_cli_operand <<function>> {
    + parse_cli_operand(operand_str: str): Union[int, float]
  }
  class run_cli <<function>> {
    + run_cli(argv: list[str] | None = None): int
  }
}

package "interactive (module)" {
  class parse_operand <<function>> {
    + parse_operand(user_input: str): Union[int, float]
  }
  class run_interactive_session <<function>> {
    + run_interactive_session(calculator: Calculator = None): None
  }
}

package "__main__ (module)" {
  class main <<function>> {
    + main(): None
  }
}

OperationRegistry *--> Calculator : holds instance

run_cli --> Calculator : instantiates
run_cli --> OperationRegistry : instantiates
run_cli ..> parse_cli_operand : calls per operand

run_interactive_session --> Calculator : creates if None
run_interactive_session --> OperationRegistry : instantiates
run_interactive_session ..> parse_operand : calls per operand

main ..> run_interactive_session : calls

note right of run_cli
  Returns 0 on success.
  Returns 1 on any error
  (prints to stderr).
end note

@enduml
